name: SeekBroadband
tag_list: broadband, mobile-broadband, adsl, isp, hsdpa, 3g, internet, comparison, broadband-offers, broadband-advice, broadband-comparison
overview:
SeekBroadband provides information, advice and a price comparison of broadband services in the UK.

The website also features a news section, unbiased user reviews, user polls, information about broadband providers in the UK, hardware information and articles to help users understand about broadband in the UK.

A price comparison service of fixed-line and mobile broadband services in the UK is available.

In addition, SeekBroadband actively gets involved in industry related issues, as well as providing comments and quotes for journalists that are covering news stories.
